controller

Class PeriCATControllerBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.PeriCATControllerBuilder

  • public class PeriCATControllerBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Builder of the builder pattern for the PeriCATController of this program. Takes all user configurations and configures the controller at program start.
